name: Machiavelli Ristorante Italiano
notes: Authentic Italian restaurant serving a traditional Neapolitan cuisine. The Linguine Gamberi was good value but a little bland in flavour.

name: Yasaka Ramen
notes: Apparently one of Sydney's best ramen eateries. Located in World Square near lightrail. Keen to try it out.

name: Mappen
notes: Fast and delicious yet very cheap. Get's crowded often, make sure to book in advance.

name: Lorraine's Patisserie
address: Shop 5, Palings Lane, 320 George St, Sydney NSW 2000
notes: Fast and delicious yet very cheap. Get's crowded often, make sure to book in advance.

name: Workshop Espresso
address: Shop 5, Palings Lane, 320 George St, Sydney NSW 2000
notes: Sandwiches and pastries in a snug, trendy cafe with timber fixtures, stools and a communal bench.
